    Deprecated. 
    This module will be discontinued, along with its classes and methods.

    @Beta
 @Deprecated
public enum LeonardoMlServiceType
extends Enum<LeonardoMlServiceType>
    There are two kinds of service types in Leonardo ML Foundation on Cloud Foundry: The Cloud Foundry service type and the Leonardo ML Foundation service type. Leonardo ML Foundation doesn't supply each of its services as individual Cloud Foundry services, but one Cloud Foundry service wrapping all Leonardo ML Services with their URLs listed in the credentials part of the Cloud Foundry service. The service url key is the property name for the url entry for a Leonardo ML Service's url entry in the credentials.

    See the 'Environment Variables' section in an application with a Leonardo ML Service binding to see the raw information.

    Be aware that this class is in Beta (as indicated by the annotation) and therefore subject to breaking changes.
